		padding-bottom: 50px;
		background-color: #a014be;
		height: 100%;
		color:white;
		font-family: 'Roboto', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
		font-weight: lighter;
	}
	hr {
		border: 0;
		clear:both;
		display:block;
		width: 76%;               
		background-color:white;
